        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Using this method, the delegate can change the menu by adding, removing, or modifying menu items. If populating the menu will take a long time, implement "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmenudelegate/1518242-numberofitemsinmenu"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmenudelegate/1518256-menu"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Menu item validation occurs after this method is called. If the menu is updated because the user pressed a command key, only the menu item with the matching command key is validated; if the menu is updated because the user opened it, then every menu item is validated."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
